    <!-- Start of the left column html code -- corresponding css in user_profile.scss
    + button will take you to the "your stories" page
    >> button takes you to that story's page
    description of what the buttons do will come up on hover
    Headers are text placeholders and I will most likely replace them with an image header.
    Hearts under story name should indicate how many likes that story has
    Book indicates how many contributions there are
    Both tell you what they mean on hover.
  -->
    <main>
      <section class="left_column">
      <div class="user_profile">
        <img src="https://w0.peakpx.com/wallpaper/335/727/HD-wallpaper-fantasy-forest-forest-tree-fantasy-green-lush-beautiful-landscape.jpg" class="user_image">
        <div class="user_info">
