                <p id="story_title"><img src="">[insert story title]</p>
                <p>20 <i class="fa-solid fa-heart" title="likes"></i></p>
                <p>2 <i class="fa-solid fa-book" title="contributions"></i></p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="story_blurb">We have nothing to speak about. There never was. Words are an unnecessary trouble. Expression is time wasting away. Any communication is just a yelp in the darkness. I am speaking now but I am saying nothing. I am just making noises, and, as it happens, they are organized in words and you should not draw meaning from this.</div>
            <footer class="feature_story_footer"><a href="/story_id"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus" title="view all of your stories"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-angles-right" title="read the whole story"></i></a></footer>
    </section>
    <img src="https://static.thenounproject.com/png/1206847-200.png" class="divider">
